name: Air Canada 767-300ER Snowy Landing at Calgary ᴴᴰ
description:
Hey everybody, since all the New Year's stuff is over, let's get back to the plane spotting! For today's video we have an Air Canada Boeing 767-300ER landing at Calgary International on Runway 35L. Videos from now on will be brand new footage from 2014, with the exception of Paine Field videos. Hope you guys enjoy!

Thanks for watching! Please comment, rate, and subscribe!
